            <li>You'll only see content that belongs to that universe</li>
            <li>Your sidebar, searches, and content lists are filtered to that world</li>
            <li>Any new content you create will automatically be added to that universe</li>
            <li>You can work on one world at a time without distractions from other projects</li>
